---
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Why It Matters</div>
    <h2>Agencies growing consistently aren't doing more marketing.</h2>
    <div class="matters-content">
      <div class="matters-left fade-up">
        <p class="lead-text">They're tightening the system behind it.</p>
        <p>When follow-up is predictable and measurable:</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Producers sell more</h4>
              <p>Structured follow-up removes guesswork and keeps deals moving.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 17H7v-7h2v7zm4 0h-2V7h2v10zm4 0h-2v-4h2v4z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Marketing becomes accountable</h4>
              <p>Every dollar spent maps to a measurable outcome.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Growth becomes intentional</h4>
              <p>Instead of hoping for results, you engineer them.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="matters-visual fade-up">
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-header">
            <span class="visual-dot red"></span>
            <span class="visual-dot yellow"></span>
            <span class="visual-dot green"></span>
            <span class="visual-title">Revenue Pipeline</span>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-bars">
            <div class="bar-row">
              <span class="bar-label">Leads In</span>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill blue" style="width: 90%"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bar-row">
              <span class="bar-label">Followed Up</span>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill orange" style="width: 40%"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bar-row">
              <span class="bar-label">Quoted</span>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill orange" style="width: 25%"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bar-row">
              <span class="bar-label">Won</span>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill green" style="width: 12%"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-gap-label">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="#ef4444"><path d="M1 21h22L12 2 1 21zm12-3h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-4h2v4z"/></svg>
            The gap between "Leads In" and "Followed Up" is where revenue leaks.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lead-text {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .matters-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .matters-left > p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .benefit-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .benefit-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .benefit-icon svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: var(--orange);
  }

  .benefit-list h4 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .benefit-list p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* Pipeline Visual */
  .visual-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  }

  .visual-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .visual-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .visual-dot.red { background: #ef4444; }
  .visual-dot.yellow { background: #facc15; }
  .visual-dot.green { background: #22c55e; }

  .visual-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  .visual-bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .bar-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .bar-label {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 90px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .bar-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 24px;
    background: #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }

  .bar-fill.blue { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3350, #293f50); }
  .bar-fill.orange { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d96d10, #f48021); }
  .bar-fill.green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #16a34a, #22c55e); }

  .visual-gap-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.4;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .visual-gap-label svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .matters-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
